<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7670> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7670" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 63; see MRR 2.491. He is perhaps to be identified with A. Fulvius A. f. Tro. in Pompeius Strabo's consilium in 89 (Cichorius, RS 175; see now Criniti, L'Epigrafe di Asculum 21, 165-166). (LRT)\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6876> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6876" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 63, who put his son to death for following Catiline (Sall. Cat. 39; Val. Max. 5.8.5; Dio 37.36, who calls the son Aulus). See RE, on M. Fulvius Nobilior, no. 94." .
